WEBVTT

00:00:08.479 --> 00:00:11.395 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
OK, kids, it’s time
to practice our Bible books!

00:00:11.395 --> 00:00:13.479 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Are you ready to try
the Christian Greek Scriptures?

00:00:13.479 --> 00:00:15.187 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Ready!

00:00:15.187 --> 00:00:20.145 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Matthew!
How Jesus came to earth and taught us all.

00:00:20.145 --> 00:00:25.062 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Mark!
Miracles showed Jesus is God’s Son.

00:00:25.062 --> 00:00:29.937 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Luke!
We can learn from all the stories Jesus told.

00:00:29.937 --> 00:00:34.812 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
John!
Like Lazarus, the dead can live again.

00:00:34.812 --> 00:00:39.729 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Acts!
How Kingdom preaching spread throughout the world.

00:00:39.729 --> 00:00:44.062 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Romans!
Explaining how God’s mercy reaches all.

00:00:44.062 --> 00:00:48.895 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
First Corinthians!
It teaches us what true love really is.

00:00:48.895 --> 00:00:54.187 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Second Corinthians!
God loves us when we’re willing to forgive.

00:00:54.187 --> 00:00:59.104 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Galatians!
Do good to everyone, and don’t give up.

00:00:59.104 --> 00:01:04.229 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Ephesians!
It teaches us how family life should be.

00:01:04.229 --> 00:01:09.062 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Philippians!
Keep focused on what’s true and good and right.

00:01:09.062 --> 00:01:13.354 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Colossians!
Obedience brings joy, as you’ll see.

00:01:13.354 --> 00:01:18.312 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
First Thessalonians!
Anytime, anywhere, we can pray.

00:01:18.312 --> 00:01:23.520 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Second Thessalonians!
No matter what, Jehovah helps his friends.

00:01:23.520 --> 00:01:28.729 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
First Timothy!
He knew the Holy Scriptures from his youth.

00:01:28.729 --> 00:01:33.645 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Second Timothy!
He bravely helped the congregation grow.

00:01:33.645 --> 00:01:38.520 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Titus!
The elders need to know how much we care.

00:01:38.520 --> 00:01:43.479 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Philemon!
His former slave became his Christian friend.

00:01:43.479 --> 00:01:48.354 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Hebrews!
We need our weekly meetings, one and all.

00:01:48.354 --> 00:01:53.229 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
James!
All good gifts and perfect presents come from God.

00:01:53.229 --> 00:01:57.812 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
First Peter!
Christ left a model we must imitate.

00:01:57.812 --> 00:02:02.687 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Second Peter!
Jehovah wants his people to be clean.

00:02:02.687 --> 00:02:07.604 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
First John!
We prove our love for God when we obey.

00:02:07.604 --> 00:02:12.520 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Second John!
Keep walking in the truth with loyalty.

00:02:12.520 --> 00:02:17.729 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Third John!
Keep showing Christian hospitality.

00:02:17.729 --> 00:02:19.854 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jude!
Don’t let Satan win.

00:02:19.854 --> 00:02:22.270 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Let’s fight to do what’s right.

00:02:22.270 --> 00:02:27.104 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Revelation!
Tells how the Paradise will come to be.

00:02:27.104 --> 00:02:31.854 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The Bible
is the greatest book of all.

00:02:31.854 --> 00:02:36.645 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah
is its Author, you’ll recall.

00:02:36.645 --> 00:02:41.729 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Let’s read it ev’ry day
to learn it and obey.

00:02:41.729 --> 00:02:45.854 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The Bible
is the greatest book of all.

